20 SECTION 2.
21 Chapter 1 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to general
22 provisions regarding state government, is amended by adding a new Code section to read as
23 follows:
24 "50-1-14.
25 The City of Incheon, South Korea is designated as the official sister city-state of the State
26 of Georgia."
27 SECTION 3.
28 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
